sentence: The Dark Star St. Stephen pairing was taken from the February 27, 1969 show at the The Fillmore; The Eleven and Turn On Your Love Light were from the January 26, 1969 show at the Avalon Ballroom; Death Don 't Have No Mercy, Feedback, and And We Bid You Goodnight were recorded March 2, 1969, at the The Fillmore.
